            span.spr Programming is magic. It's the ability to create things from pure imagination. We started CodeCombat to give learners the feeling of wizardly power at their fingertips, straight from the first keystroke. With game-based learning, players not only get more excited about computer science, but they learn faster, too. Way faster. It's like having a conversation instead of reading a book. We want to bring that conversation to every school and to every student, because we believe that everyone should have a chance to become a native speaker of code.

